  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The request of the tri-army to the people of the country!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Triforce appealed to the people of the country to support the army and police to maintain peace in the country.",
        "Chief of Defense Forces General Shavendra Silva further informed about this,",
        "At this moment when the opportunity has arisen to solve the crisis situation in the country in a peaceful manner and according to the constitution, he said that he requested the people to support the army and police to maintain the peace of the country."
      ],
